<plot>Nisha (Raakhee) is an accomplished and much sought after professional Architect. She is reclusive after the tragic death of her boyfriend, Shashi Saigal (Shashi Kapoor). When Karan Saxena (Rishi Kapoor) offers her employment with his advertising agency, she accepts. Only she knows that the reason of accepting this employment offer is that Karan, newly married, resembles Shashi a lot, and she will anything in her power to make him her's.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?156386</url></doc>
